definitions.definition: Any one out of an indefinite number of persons ; anyone ; any person .
A person of some consideration or standing .
examples: Everybody who wants to be anybody will come to Jake's party.
Here one isn't anybody , if one doesn't dance like Travolta.

main_definition: Any one out of an indefinite number of persons ; anyone ; any person .
secondary_definitions: ( informal ) A person of some consideration or standing .
